{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778977118253,"sessionID":"ses_1ccb84d98ffeWH3ShOq9EHPmcq","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_Fx9a16R1JphAKWDFv0VpFL5X","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Implemented the requested HRA/HuBMAP terms and committed the changes locally.\n+\n+Added the salivary gland ducto-acinar unit hierarchy, including the three gland-specific terms, and added dentogingival junction with \"gingival attachment\" retained as a related synonym. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n*** Add File: PR_COMMENTS.md\n+## Summary\n+\n+This change addresses issue #3657 by adding five new HRA/HuBMAP-requested UBERON terms:\n+\n+- `UBERON:9900001` salivary gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900002` parotid gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900003` sublingual gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900004` submandibular gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900005` dentogingival junction\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion clarified that \"ducto-acinar\" refers to a multicellular salivary gland functional tissue unit, not a cell type or a simple acinus-duct junction. I modeled the generic salivary gland ducto-acinar unit as a `lobule` and placed the gland-specific terms beneath it with `part_of` relationships to the appropriate major salivary glands.\n+\n+For the requested \"gingival attachment\" concept, the issue discussion clarified that the intended concept is the broader dentogingival/periodontal attachment apparatus rather than attached gingiva or gingival epithelium alone. I used `dentogingival junction` as the preferred label and retained `gingival attachment`, `dentogingival complex`, and `supracrestal tissue attachment` as related synonyms.\n+\n+## Metadata\n+\n+All new terms include:\n+\n+- `subset: added_by_HRA`\n+- contributor attribution to `https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2999-0103`\n+- `dcterms-date`\n+- `term_tracker_item` pointing to issue #3657\n+- `created_by: dragon-ai-agent`\n+- definitions with source xrefs\n+\n+## Validation Checklist\n+\n+- Read and reviewed imported issue title, body, and comments from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked for existing UBERON terms for `ducto-acinar`, `salivon`, `dentogingival`, and `gingival attachment`; no existing matching terms were found.\n+- Verified requested parent terms with `obo-grep.pl`: parotid gland, sublingual gland, submandibular gland, gingiva, lobule, and saliva-secreting gland.\n+- Reviewed the NCBI Bookshelf salivary gland source and PubMed records for PMID:24862590, PMID:30855909, and PMID:38876998.\n+- Added terms via the `terms/` checkout/checkin workflow using `obo-checkin.pl`.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Ran `robot convert` syntax validation successfully.\n+- Ran `robot reason --reasoner ELK` successfully.\n+\n+## Notes\n+\n+The `aurelian` command mentioned in the project instructions was not available in this local environment, so publication validation was performed with PubMed/NCBI web lookups instead.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+Implemented the requested HRA/HuBMAP terms and committed the changes locally.\n+\n+Added the salivary gland ducto-acinar unit hierarchy, including the three gland-specific terms, and added dentogingival junction with \"gingival attachment\" retained as a related synonym. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,41 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+This change addresses issue #3657 by adding five new HRA/HuBMAP-requested UBERON terms:\n+\n+- `UBERON:9900001` salivary gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900002` parotid gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900003` sublingual gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900004` submandibular gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900005` dentogingival junction\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion clarified that \"ducto-acinar\" refers to a multicellular salivary gland functional tissue unit, not a cell type or a simple acinus-duct junction. I modeled the generic salivary gland ducto-acinar unit as a `lobule` and placed the gland-specific terms beneath it with `part_of` relationships to the appropriate major salivary glands.\n+\n+For the requested \"gingival attachment\" concept, the issue discussion clarified that the intended concept is the broader dentogingival/periodontal attachment apparatus rather than attached gingiva or gingival epithelium alone. I used `dentogingival junction` as the preferred label and retained `gingival attachment`, `dentogingival complex`, and `supracrestal tissue attachment` as related synonyms.\n+\n+## Metadata\n+\n+All new terms include:\n+\n+- `subset: added_by_HRA`\n+- contributor attribution to `https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2999-0103`\n+- `dcterms-date`\n+- `term_tracker_item` pointing to issue #3657\n+- `created_by: dragon-ai-agent`\n+- definitions with source xrefs\n+\n+## Validation Checklist\n+\n+- Read and reviewed imported issue title, body, and comments from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked for existing UBERON terms for `ducto-acinar`, `salivon`, `dentogingival`, and `gingival attachment`; no existing matching terms were found.\n+- Verified requested parent terms with `obo-grep.pl`: parotid gland, sublingual gland, submandibular gland, gingiva, lobule, and saliva-secreting gland.\n+- Reviewed the NCBI Bookshelf salivary gland source and PubMed records for PMID:24862590, PMID:30855909, and PMID:38876998.\n+- Added terms via the `terms/` checkout/checkin workflow using `obo-checkin.pl`.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Ran `robot convert` syntax validation successfully.\n+- Ran `robot reason --reasoner ELK` successfully.\n+\n+## Notes\n+\n+The `aurelian` command mentioned in the project instructions was not available in this local environment, so publication validation was performed with PubMed/NCBI web lookups instead.\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"ISSUE_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+Implemented the requested HRA/HuBMAP terms and committed the changes locally.\n+\n+Added the salivary gland ducto-acinar unit hierarchy, including the three gland-specific terms, and added dentogingival junction with \"gingival attachment\" retained as a related synonym. Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n","additions":3,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md","relativePath":"PR_COMMENTS.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,41 @@\n+## Summary\n+\n+This change addresses issue #3657 by adding five new HRA/HuBMAP-requested UBERON terms:\n+\n+- `UBERON:9900001` salivary gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900002` parotid gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900003` sublingual gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900004` submandibular gland ducto-acinar unit\n+- `UBERON:9900005` dentogingival junction\n+\n+## Rationale\n+\n+The issue discussion clarified that \"ducto-acinar\" refers to a multicellular salivary gland functional tissue unit, not a cell type or a simple acinus-duct junction. I modeled the generic salivary gland ducto-acinar unit as a `lobule` and placed the gland-specific terms beneath it with `part_of` relationships to the appropriate major salivary glands.\n+\n+For the requested \"gingival attachment\" concept, the issue discussion clarified that the intended concept is the broader dentogingival/periodontal attachment apparatus rather than attached gingiva or gingival epithelium alone. I used `dentogingival junction` as the preferred label and retained `gingival attachment`, `dentogingival complex`, and `supracrestal tissue attachment` as related synonyms.\n+\n+## Metadata\n+\n+All new terms include:\n+\n+- `subset: added_by_HRA`\n+- contributor attribution to `https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2999-0103`\n+- `dcterms-date`\n+- `term_tracker_item` pointing to issue #3657\n+- `created_by: dragon-ai-agent`\n+- definitions with source xrefs\n+\n+## Validation Checklist\n+\n+- Read and reviewed imported issue title, body, and comments from `__issue_context__.json`.\n+- Checked for existing UBERON terms for `ducto-acinar`, `salivon`, `dentogingival`, and `gingival attachment`; no existing matching terms were found.\n+- Verified requested parent terms with `obo-grep.pl`: parotid gland, sublingual gland, submandibular gland, gingiva, lobule, and saliva-secreting gland.\n+- Reviewed the NCBI Bookshelf salivary gland source and PubMed records for PMID:24862590, PMID:30855909, and PMID:38876998.\n+- Added terms via the `terms/` checkout/checkin workflow using `obo-checkin.pl`.\n+- Reserialized `src/ontology/uberon-edit.obo` with `robot convert`.\n+- Ran `robot convert` syntax validation successfully.\n+- Ran `robot reason --reasoner ELK` successfully.\n+\n+## Notes\n+\n+The `aurelian` command mentioned in the project instructions was not available in this local environment, so publication validation was performed with PubMed/NCBI web lookups instead.\n","additions":41,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","time":{"start":1778977118244,"end":1778977118251}},"id":"prt_e334c6284001z1YLmA15mtBdSp","sessionID":"ses_1ccb84d98ffeWH3ShOq9EHPmcq","messageID":"msg_e334c564d001S3aeAdQ2FLxZQy"}}
